OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777551071
OL,3,CPolice cordon in Plymouth after
OL,4,Csuspected World War 2 bomb discovered
OL,6,FA 200m police cordon is in place
OL,7,Faround a building site in the Southway
OL,8,Farea of Plymouth after a "suspected
OL,9,FWorld War 2 bomb" was discovered.
OL,11,FDevon and Cornwall Police have
OL,12,Fconfirmed the suspected bomb was found
OL,13,Fduring building works this afternoon
OL,14,F(29 April).
OL,16,FThe Royal Navy's Explosives Ordnance
OL,17,FDepartment is now at the scene to
OL,18,F'assess the item'.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
