OL,3,CPolice cordon in Plymouth after
OL,4,Csuspected World War 2 bomb discovered
OL,6,FA cordon is in place at Flamborough
OL,7,FRoad and several roads in the area
OL,8,Fhave also been closed.
OL,10,FPlymouth City Council have said: "We
OL,11,Fwould like to reassure the community
OL,12,Fthat this is a precautionary measure
OL,13,Fand there is no immediate risk to the
OL,14,Fwider public. We are asking people to
OL,15,Fplease avoid the area while this work
OL,16,Fcontinues."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
