OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777551071
OL,3,CPolice cordon in Plymouth after
OL,4,Csuspected World War 2 bomb discovered
OL,6,F"Residents who have been temporarily
OL,7,Fdisplaced as a result of the cordon
OL,8,Fcan go to Southway youth centre, where
OL,9,Fcouncil and Plymouth Community Homes
OL,10,Fstaff are available to offer support,
OL,11,Finformation and practical assistance."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
